Enclosing class:
Type
public static class Type.NoType
extends GType
implements Type

A Type that represents a user interface state in which the user has neglected to set a type on a particular field, or has removed a type without replacing it. Decaf does not apply any default for types (except in the case of the method return type, which defaults to VoidType).
